            <history-note id="DLM1108775"><amended-provision>Section 2</amended-provision>: <amending-provision href="DLM1662482">subparts 1</amending-provision> and <amending-provision href="DLM1662498">2</amending-provision> of Part 2 and <amending-provision href="DLM160003">sections 50(1)(a) and (c)–(h)</amending-provision> and <amending-provision href="DLM160010">51</amending-provision> <amending-operation>brought into force</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>19 November 2007</amendment-date>, by the <amending-provision href="DLM981493">Climate Change Response Act Commencement Order 2007</amending-provision> <amending-leg/> (SR 2007/336).</history-note>
          </history>
        </notes>
