              <history-note id="DLM1666009"><amended-provision>Section 189</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>added</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>26 September 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1131123">section 50</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Climate Change Response (Emissions Trading) Amendment Act 2008</amending-leg> (2008 No 85).</history-note>
