        <prov id="DLM1662802" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">197</label>
          <heading>First emissions return for post-1989 forest land activities</heading>
          <prov.body>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
              <para>
                <text>Despite anything in this Act, the first emissions return submitted by a person to whom <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM1662782">section 189</intref></citation> applies in respect of an activity listed in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM1662865">Part 1</intref> of Schedule 4</citation> may not be submitted before 1 January 2009.</text>
              </para>
            </subprov>
          </prov.body>
          <notes>
            <history>
              <history-note id="DLM1666019"><amended-provision>Section 197</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>added</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>26 September 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1131123">section 50</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Climate Change Response (Emissions Trading) Amendment Act 2008</amending-leg> (2008 No 85).</history-note>
            </history>
          </notes>
        </prov>
